      "error_note": "",
      "severity": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "eq_2693",
      "raw": "A * rho_+ = rho_+ * A  (A commutes with Psi_+ gauge action)",
      "type": "comment",
      "context": "From condition 1: T must commute with rho_full(v) = diag(rho_+, rho_-). This means:",
